                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250407-247-victim1263 t18250407-247-viclabel1331"></join>. On the 7th of April the prisoner and another came into the shop; while I was bargaining with one of them, the other stole the coat; the officer brought the prisoner in with the coat within a minute after they had left - it had been in the window, and within their reach.</p>
